  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Mohsus darrija weenu\nTschuhſchku no Warra/ un uhs-\nzehle to par weenu Sihmi/ un\ntas notikke/ ja fahda Tschuhſchka\njebkuren bij kohduſi/ tas uhsſuh-\nkoja to Tschuhſchku no Warra/\nun palikke Dſihws.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad aisgahje tee Israëta\nBehrni/ un apinettahs Obotâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz to aisgahje tee no\nObota/ un apmettahs pee teem\nPaſkalneem Abarim Tuksnefi/kas\nprett Moabu irr prett Rihteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No turrenes aisgahje tee/\nun apmettahs pee tahs Saredas\nUppes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No turrenes aisgahje tee/\nun apmettahs schai Arnonsa Puſ-\nfê/ kas Tuksneſi irr/ iſeedami\nno to Amoriteeu Rohbeschas/ jo\nArnons irr Moaba Rohbescha /\nstarp Moabu/ un starp teem A-\nmoritexeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "( Tapehz tohp fazzihts/\neekſch tahs Karrn-Grahmatas ta\nKUNGA; ( tas KUNGS\nkarroja) prett Waebu zaur Wee-\nfuli/ un prett tahm Arnonsa\nUppehin. )\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas ( Arnons )\nStrautu Awohts lohkahs ap to\nWiddu Ar/ un tohp faliſts ar\nMoaba Rohbeschahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no turrenes aisgahje\ntee us Beërnu / tchi irr ta Akka/\nno ka tas KUNGS us Mobsu\nfazzija: Sapulzina tohs Laudis/\ntad es juuns dohſchn Uhdeni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad dseedaja Israëls fcho\nDseesimu: Uhslezz tu Akka/ dsee-\ndajeet no tahs weens prett ohtru:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu Akka/ ko tee Wirfnee-\nki irr rakkuſchi/ ko to Lauschu\nJeenigee irr tsbedduschi zaur to\nBauſlibas-Deweju/ ar farveem\nSisleem. Pehz to aisgahje tee\nno tahs Tuksnefes uhs Matanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Matanas uhs Na-\nalieli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Naaliela uhs Ba-\nmotu/ un no Bamotas uhs to\nEeleju/ kas Moaba Laukâ irr/\npee to angstu Kalnu Pisga/ kas\nprett to Tuksnibu steepjahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fuhtija Israëls Weh-\nſtis us Sionu / to Amoriteru\nKehnizu/ un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lat es zaur tawu Semmi\neenu/ mehs ne greesifinees Dru-\nwês/neds Wihna-Duhrsôs/mehs\nne Dserﬁm to Uhdeni no Akkahm/\npa Leel-Zettu eſtim mehs/ tee-\nkams mehs zaur tawahm Rohbe-\nschahm zaurgahjnschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Sions ne fahwe I-\nsraëln zaur fawahm Rohbe-\nschahm eet/ un Sions fapulzeja s\nwiﬀus fawus Laudis/un aisgah-\nje Israëtam pretti us to Tuks-\nnefi/ un wiꞥſch nahze us Jakzu/\nun karroja prett Israëlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Israëls apkawe win-\nuu ar ta Sobbiha Asmini/ un Jo\nuemanteja winna Semmi/ no\nArnons lihds Jabokam/ lihds\nAmmons Behrneem/(jo Ammo-\nna BehrnuRohbeschah vija fitpra.)\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta nehme Israëls wiﬀus\n"
    }
  ],
